<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>주문 확인</title>
    <style>
        /* 전체 기본 스타일 초기화 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* 상단 헤더 & 네비게이션 바 */
        .header-bar {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .header-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .logo-area h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #111;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .menu-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .menu-links a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .menu-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .user-status {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #495057;
            background-color: #f1f3f5;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }

        /* 주문완료 메인 박스 */
        .order-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .order-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* 성공 체크 아이콘 */
        .success-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #e6f4ea;
            color: #137333;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .order-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }

        .order-subtitle {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
        }

        /* 영수증 내역 테이블 상자 */
        .receipt-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .receipt-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* 주문된 아이템 리스트 정보 */
        .receipt-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #212529;
        }

        .receipt-item .item-qty {
            color: #868e96;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-left: 6px;
        }

        /* 최종 결제액 강조 라인 */
        .receipt-total {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ced4da;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .total-amount {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #e03131;
        }

        /* 버튼 제어 */
        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header-bar">
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="logo-area">
                <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <h1>💻 내 쇼핑몰</h1>
                </a>
                <div class="menu-links">
                    <a href="/">상품목록</a>
                    <a href="/cart">장바구니</a>
                    <a href="/board">고객센터</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="user-status">
                👋 <strong><%= user ? (user.username || user.id) : '고객' %>님</strong> 환영합니다!
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="order-container">
        <div class="order-card">

            <div class="success-icon">✓</div>

            <h2 class="order-title">주문이 정상 완료되었습니다!</h2>
            <p class="order-subtitle">저희 쇼핑몰을 이용해 주셔서 진심으로 감사드립니다.</p>

            <div class="receipt-box">
                <div class="receipt-title">📋 주문 상품 요약</div>

                <% if (typeof items !== 'undefined' && items && items.length > 0) { %>
                    <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                        <div class="receipt-item">
                            <div>
                                <span>💻 <%= item.name %></span>
                                <span class="item-qty">(<%= item.quantity %>개)</span>
                            </div>
                            <span>₩<%= (item.price * item.quantity).toLocaleString() %></span>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="receipt-item">
                        <div>🛍️ 주문 상품</div>
                        <span>결제 완료</span>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="receipt-total">
                    <span>최종 결제 금액</span>
                    <span class="total-amount">
                        <%= typeof total !== 'undefined' && total ? total.toLocaleString() : '0' %>원
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/" class="btn-home">🛍️ 쇼핑 계속하기</a>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>